name: DineOnCampus
0:
”Alexa, ask dine on campus what's for lunch at dining commons at San Jose State University.”
”Alexa, ask Dine on Campus what is Foster Walker at Northwestern University serving for dinner tomorrow.”
”Alexa, ask Dine on Campus what is The Works at University of Nevada Reno serving for lunch.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dine on campus
Developer Terms of Use
des: Use Dine On Campus for Alexa to find out what your school's dining locations will have on the menu. Just provide Alexa with your school's name, the dining location you are inquiring about, the meal period, and an optional date, and Alexa will tell you what is on the menu.
priv:
Developer Privacy Policy
The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
